    PRODI ||--o{ MATERIAL_REQUEST : "receives"
    PRODI ||--o{ EXERCISE : "has"
    USER ||--o{ MATERIAL : "uploads"
    USER ||--o{ VIDEO : "uploads"
    USER ||--o{ RESPONSI : "creates"
    USER ||--o{ MATERIAL_REQUEST : "submits"
    USER ||--o{ EXERCISE : "creates"
    USER ||--o{ ACTIVITY_LOG : "generates"
    VIDEO ||--o| RESPONSI : "linked to"
```

