## 7. Tech Stack & Arsitektur

### 7.1 Stack Overview

| Layer | Teknologi | Keterangan |
|---|---|---|
| **Frontend** | Next.js (App Router) | SSR/CSR, React-based |
| **Backend** | ElysiaJS (Bun runtime) | REST API, type-safe |
| **Database** | PostgreSQL | Relational, ACID-compliant |
| **ORM** | Drizzle ORM / Prisma | Type-safe query builder |
| **Auth** | JWT (Access + Refresh Token) | Stateless authentication |
| **File Storage** | Local / Cloud (S3/Supabase Storage) | Untuk materi PDF/Excel/dll |
| **Video** | YouTube iFrame API | Embedded player, unlisted videos |

### 7.2 Arsitektur Sistem

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph Frontend ["Frontend (Next.js)"]
        UI[React Components]
        Pages[App Router Pages]
        API_Client[API Client / Fetch]
    end

    subgraph Backend ["Backend (ElysiaJS)"]
        Routes[API Routes]
        Middleware[Auth & RBAC Middleware]
        Controllers[Controllers]
        Services[Business Logic]
    end

    subgraph Database ["Database (PostgreSQL)"]
        Tables[(Tables)]
    end

    subgraph External ["External Services"]
        YT[YouTube iFrame API]
        GF[Google Forms]
        Storage[File Storage]
    end

    UI --> Pages --> API_Client
    API_Client -->|REST API| Routes
    Routes --> Middleware --> Controllers --> Services
    Services --> Tables
    Services --> Storage
    UI --> YT
    UI --> GF
```

---

## 8. Keamanan & Otorisasi

### 8.1 Autentikasi
- Login menggunakan email & password
- JWT-based authentication (Access Token + Refresh Token)
- Access Token: short-lived (15 menit)
- Refresh Token: long-lived (7 hari), disimpan di httpOnly cookie

### 8.2 Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)

| Resource | Super Admin | Admin (Own Prodi) | Admin (Other Prodi) | Student |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Materi** | Full CRUD (All) | Full CRUD | Read Only | Read + Download |
| **Video** | Full CRUD (All) | Full CRUD | Read Only | Watch Only |
| **Responsi** | Full CRUD (All) | Full CRUD | Read Only | Read Only |
| **Latihan Soal** | Full CRUD (All) | Full CRUD | Read Only | Access (Redirect) |
| **Request Materi** | View All | Manage (Own Prodi) | — | Submit + View Own |
| **User Management** | Full CRUD | — | — | — |
| **Log Activity** | Full Access | — | — | — |

---

## 9. Non-Functional Requirements

| Aspek | Requirement |
|---|---|
| **Performance** | Halaman load < 3 detik, API response < 500ms |
| **Responsive** | Mendukung desktop, tablet, dan mobile |
| **Browser Support** | Chrome, Firefox, Edge, Safari (versi terbaru) |
| **Scalability** | Mendukung minimal 500 concurrent users |
| **Availability** | Target uptime 99% |
| **Data Backup** | Backup database harian |

---

## 10. Milestone & Timeline (Estimasi)

| Phase | Durasi | Deliverable |
|---|---|---|
| **Phase 1 — Foundation** | 2 minggu | Setup project, auth, user management, database schema |
| **Phase 2 — Core Features** | 3 minggu | Materi, video, responsi, latihan soal |
| **Phase 3 — Advanced Features** | 2 minggu | Request materi, log activity, dashboard analytics |
| **Phase 4 — Polish & Testing** | 1 minggu | UI polish, testing, bug fixing, optimization |
| **Phase 5 — Deployment** | 1 minggu | Deployment, monitoring setup, documentation |

> [!NOTE]
> Timeline bersifat estimasi dan dapat disesuaikan berdasarkan kompleksitas implementasi.

---

## 11. Risiko & Mitigasi

| Risiko | Dampak | Mitigasi |
|---|---|---|
| Video YouTube unlisted bisa dibagikan link-nya | Konten bocor di luar platform | Implementasi domain restriction pada YouTube API, rotasi link jika perlu |
| File storage membengkak | Cost & performance | Set max file size, implementasi auto-cleanup, gunakan cloud storage |
| Concurrent live streaming load | Server overload | YouTube menangani streaming, HelPhin hanya embed — risiko rendah |
| Data breach | Keamanan terkompromi | Enkripsi password (bcrypt), HTTPS, validasi input, rate limiting |

---

## 12. Glosarium

| Istilah | Definisi |
|---|---|
| **Responsi** | Sesi tutorial/review akademik yang dipandu oleh mahasiswa senior atau asisten |
| **Prodi** | Program Studi — unit akademik di bawah fakultas |
| **Himpunan** | Himpunan Mahasiswa — organisasi kemahasiswaan per prodi |
| **LMS** | Learning Management System — platform pengelolaan pembelajaran |
| **RBAC** | Role-Based Access Control — kontrol akses berbasis peran |
